_aFiles._sDescription: This is the version ready for gamebanana.

_sText:
This map is deliberately hard, confusing, and poorly spaced. You will have trouble in your first few minutes in this map. It is not long, but most "problems" are deliberate. There are 2 intentional skips and 1 unintentional skip. If your run uses the unintentional skip it probably won't get accepted by SJ or Faste.

Please contact me if there are any REAL problems with the map, I.E. bugs, glitches, etc.
